#
# WARNING: Anything that is not a `*.java' file in `src/'
# directory will get rejected at an attempt to push to the
# server. (This is a server-side check!)
#
# 1) Ignore everything not in /src/ in project root.
# 2) ... or not in /doc/.
#

/*
!/src/
!/doc/

#
# File-type ignores; unfortunately...
#
# *
# !*.java
# !*/
#
# ... won't work in EGit (while it does in git). =/
# This also, unfortunately ignores any directory containing
# a dot `.' in its name. Adding `!*/' unignores all subdir
# contents, regardless of their extension. EGit bug that is.
#
# 2) Ignore all non-*.java files
#

*.*
!*.java

#
# LaTeX filters
#

!*.tex
!*.eps
!*.jpg
!*.png
